  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline at dusk or dawn. The scene is dominated by a vibrant and expansive sky filled with layered clouds exhibiting hues of orange, pink, and purple. Below, a sprawling urban landscape spreads towards the water, punctuated by twinkling city lights. The bay is calm and reflects the colors of the sky. Silhouettes of hills and distant structures contribute to the depth of the image. In the foreground, dark shapes of trees or vegetation are visible, providing a framing element. The overall impression is one of serene beauty and urban grandeur.",
